@aspieclaire @FloragreenFlora @ItsEmilyKaty People get hung up on ND being called "neurodiverse" bc "neurodiversity" includes ALL human brains.

Neurotypical brains + neuroDIVERGENT brains (autistic, ADHD, etc) = neurodiversity (not shouting; italics would be better than CAPS).

NDs diverge; *everyone* makes up diversity.

